84
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:33,440
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, da sam bio i preživahan.

85
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:36,240
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bih rekao da sam bio i preživahan.

86
00:08:36,879 --> 00:08:39,279
