538
00:56:21,920 --> 00:56:23,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, šta ću ono?

539
00:56:23,599 --> 00:56:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to ono.

540
00:56:25,760 --> 00:56:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] što.

541
00:56:26,079 --> 00:56:27,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ti je odgovorio na pitanje.

542
00:56:29,519 --> 00:56:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] Za te poticaje.

543
00:56:30,960 --> 00:56:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, nisam išao u široko patinu, nisam odgovorio na.

544
00:56:34,079 --> 00:56:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tu u zatvoru, jesi li se.

545
00:56:36,960 --> 00:56:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne, ti je.

546
00:56:38,880 --> 00:56:39,519
[SPEAKER_00] Imala sam ja plan.

547
00:56:39,920 --> 00:56:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] Plan je bio trening, čista glava i samo kriminal, samo prodaja.

548
00:56:49,760 --> 00:56:52,239
[SPEAKER_00] Sad idemo jako, jako.

549
00:56:53,599 --> 00:56:54,719
[SPEAKER_00] Plan mi je bio top.

550
00:56:55,920 --> 00:56:58,320
